570
00:33:43,420 --> 00:33:45,160
When Yunxi returns
to the Judicial Review,

571
00:33:45,220 --> 00:33:46,580
he'll investigate this thoroughly.

572
00:33:47,340 --> 00:33:49,300
Someone must be framing us.

