May the Bodhisattva bless us.

576
00:34:00,660 --> 00:34:01,500
Nanny Chen,

577
00:34:02,620 --> 00:34:03,780
you should leave.

578
00:34:05,460 --> 00:34:06,500
Why stay?

579
00:34:12,260 --> 00:34:13,100
Madam,

580
00:34:14,020 --> 00:34:15,140
allow me to speak

581
00:34:15,660 --> 00:34:16,780
out of turn

582
00:34:17,900 --> 00:34:19,540
and call you Xiwen.

583
00:34:20,000 --> 00:34:22,820
Back then,
the Ruan family was prominent,

584
00:34:23,500 --> 00:34:24,340
but now,

585
00:34:25,380 --> 00:34:27,580
only you and I are here.

586
00:34:28,740 --> 00:34:29,900
After all these years,

587
00:34:30,260 --> 00:34:32,660
I know that you don't just see me

588
00:34:33,100 --> 00:34:35,700
as a servant.

589
00:34:36,580 --> 00:34:38,020
If you don't mind,

590
00:34:39,180 --> 00:34:42,300
let me accompany you
on your last journey.

591
00:34:57,900 --> 00:34:58,780
Mr. Yuwen,

592
00:34:59,700 --> 00:35:00,700
where is my master?

593
00:35:00,980 --> 00:35:02,100
What does he say?

594
00:35:02,460 --> 00:35:03,980
Zhuang Shiyang refuses to admit it,

595
00:35:04,220 --> 00:35:05,540
but the evidence is irrefutable,

596
00:35:05,580 --> 00:35:06,620
so he can't deny it.

597
00:35:06,940 --> 00:35:09,140
Take account of all the Zhuangs

598
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:10,400
and bring them to prison.

599
00:35:10,460 --> 00:35:11,960
There's no need to wait until autumn.

600
00:35:12,260 --> 00:35:14,820
Execute them at the Wu hour tomorrow.

601
00:35:36,980 --> 00:35:39,300
Zhuang Shiyang, the master,

602
00:35:39,500 --> 00:35:41,140
Ms. Wei, the grandmother,

603
00:35:41,500 --> 00:35:44,060
Ruan Xiwen, the wife,

604
00:35:46,300 --> 00:35:48,460
Zhou Ruyin, the concubine,

605
00:35:48,780 --> 00:35:50,340
Zhuang Yushan, Zhou's daughter,

606
00:35:50,580 --> 00:35:52,340
Zhuang Yuchi, Zhou's son.

607
00:36:05,780 --> 00:36:07,060
There are six people

608
00:36:07,980 --> 00:36:10,260
in Zhuang Shiyang's family.
Take them away.

609
00:36:10,420 --> 00:36:11,340
What's going on?

610
00:36:12,500 --> 00:36:13,940
Why isn't Zhuang Hanyan listed?

611
00:36:14,180 --> 00:36:15,540
According to the family register,

612
00:36:15,580 --> 00:36:17,140
Zhuang Hanyan, the lineal daughter,

613
00:36:17,540 --> 00:36:20,100
was removed from the family register
two years ago

614
00:36:20,940 --> 00:36:23,860
and adopted by Zhang Youchang
from Nanzhang, Danzhou.

615
00:36:24,140 --> 00:36:25,940
She is not a Zhuang family member.

616
00:36:27,740 --> 00:36:28,580
Take them away.

617
00:36:29,540 --> 00:36:31,100
Yuchi, Yushan.

618
00:36:31,780 --> 00:36:33,440
- Yuchi, Yushan.
- Yushan.

619
00:36:35,900 --> 00:36:36,740
- Go.
- Yuchi.

620
00:37:01,980 --> 00:37:06,020
(Zhuang Hanyan, the lineal daughter,
was removed from the family register.)

621
00:37:06,220 --> 00:37:10,810
♪Listen, the wind stirs my heart♪

622
00:37:11,760 --> 00:37:14,370
♪Blurring my weary eyes♪

623
00:37:15,100 --> 00:37:17,030
♪You are my closest kin♪

624
00:37:17,980 --> 00:37:18,820
Mother,

625
00:37:21,540 --> 00:37:22,420
what is

626
00:37:24,540 --> 00:37:26,260
all this for?

627
00:37:28,060 --> 00:37:29,540
I once told you.

628
00:37:32,700 --> 00:37:35,140
When injustice falls upon you,

629
00:37:37,220 --> 00:37:38,580
endurance is painful,

630
00:37:40,940 --> 00:37:42,740
but so is resistance.

631
00:37:44,430 --> 00:37:47,680
♪Do not call me cold and cruel♪

632
00:37:49,460 --> 00:37:50,780
If you don't know the reason,

633
00:37:52,500 --> 00:37:54,500
you won't be entangled by hatred.

634
00:37:57,120 --> 00:37:58,680
♪If hatred never fades♪

635
00:37:59,980 --> 00:38:01,860
Only then can you live a good life.

636
00:38:05,060 --> 00:38:06,660
Our blood bond

637
00:38:07,360 --> 00:38:10,330
♪Ties and bonds, all too fleeting♪

638
00:38:10,380 --> 00:38:11,530
ends today.

639
00:38:11,530 --> 00:38:13,650
♪I want you to be carefree forever♪

640
00:38:13,650 --> 00:38:15,700
♪I will be carefree♪

641
00:38:16,180 --> 00:38:17,220
See you in the next life.

642
00:38:17,220 --> 00:38:18,580
♪All my wishes will be fulfilled♪

643
00:38:18,580 --> 00:38:21,840
♪Who will cut the kite's string?♪

644
00:38:21,840 --> 00:38:25,360
♪Who will mend the regrets left behind?♪

645
00:38:25,360 --> 00:38:27,070
♪Sleepless nights linger on♪

646
00:38:27,100 --> 00:38:27,980
Let's go.

647
00:38:27,980 --> 00:38:31,460
♪I seem to see you in my dreams♪

648
00:38:32,720 --> 00:38:36,090
♪Unwilling to sever the threads of fate♪

649
00:38:36,370 --> 00:38:39,810
♪Ties and bonds will remain♪

650
00:38:40,140 --> 00:38:42,800
♪I want you to be carefree forever♪

651
00:38:42,800 --> 00:38:44,160
♪I will be carefree♪

652
00:38:44,300 --> 00:38:45,740
(I am Zhuang Hanyan.)

653
00:38:46,100 --> 00:38:47,940
(Geese leave in winter
and return in spring.)

654
00:38:48,380 --> 00:38:50,380
(But I came to the north
