655
00:38:50,980 --> 00:38:54,020
(from the south.)

656
00:38:54,380 --> 00:38:56,020
(In this freezing world,)

657
00:38:56,980 --> 00:38:59,260
(I am searching for a bit of warmth,)

658
00:38:59,700 --> 00:39:01,220
(Maybe I was wrong)

659
00:39:01,780 --> 00:39:02,740
